uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.store

Interface IStoreRegenReport

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    IStoreActiveRegenReport, IStoreInertRegenReport

    public interface IStoreRegenReport
    Provides information concerning any IFrame/ISlot networks serialized on disk, that are now fully invalid or partially valid with respect to the current model. See IRegenStatus for definitions of fully invalid and partially valid networks.

    • Method Summary

      java.io.File getLogFileOrNull()
